data.text:
Normal

The team investigate the case of a serial killer who is shooting luxury car drivers on Southern California's freeways.

Parity

Sydney finds trouble in the form of her arch nemesis while in Madrid to retrieve a 500-year-old sketch, and Will investigates Danny's death.

A Broken Heart

Sydney and Dixon take on a case involving the safety of the United Commerce Organization, and Francie confronts her boyfriend about his secret meetings with a woman.

There's Only One Sydney Bristow

Sydney's maternity leave is disturbed when her enemies decide that the best way to get to her is through her friends.
